data.title: Greenwich Village Restaurant
data.meta_description: The restaurant is located on the ground level of the iconic One 5th Avenue building on the corner of E 8th Street and 5th Avenue, just north of Washington Square Park. The entrance is on 8th Street.
data.meta_site_name: Trattoria One Fifth | Italian Restaurant in New York, NY
data.text:
HOW TO GET HERE

The restaurant is located in ground level of the iconic One 5th Avenue building on the corner of E 8th Street and 5th Avenue, just north of Washington Square Park.

We are a short walk from the following train lines:

R/W - 8th Street

6 - Astor Place

A/C/E - W 4th Street

B/D/F/M - W 4th Street

Or a few blocks away from 14th Street - Union Square.
